wish to reassure our shareholders and other stakeholders including all our esteemed customers of the management’s commitment to good corporate governance and global best practices in all our dealings.”    Ardova Plc explains delay in filing 2021 audited financial reports In "Business" Stock investors gain N5.64trn in H1'22 on improved liquidity In "Business" DMO lists N250bn Sukuk on NGX In "Business"